Sey La Familia dey hoy, or today family go start dis spring, and join national bi monthly magazine, and TV programme.

Di television element of La Familia include one series of two minute information wey go reach seven days every week for di Spanish-language Univision Network, one unit of Univision Holdings Inc, wey be 80% of hallmark card inc.

Di features go include parenting, family health, nutrition, and financial management, and 30 seconds of advertising.

Di magazines also ad-... support dem go dey for more than 10,000 doctors office, clinic, and health centre for Hispanic, and mostly Hispanic communities.

